item.title: 24h Comics Square Challenge
item.description: If you ever thought about your childhood, you know how blurry the memory can be. One moment I am sure that some event happened, and the next, I can’t find any more details about it in my head. It is like I watched a video of my childhood, but it was a long time ago. And I am not really sure what happened, I can only notice the overall mood of my own childhood movie.
